# Self-host build patch: the broad **/build rule above strips fluxer_app/scripts/build,
# which the rspack config imports at build time. Re-include it. emojis.json was also
# explicitly ignored above (now removed) but is required by the app build.
!fluxer_app/scripts/build
!fluxer_app/scripts/build/**
